{"tid":774760,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港共殖民政府送出65.5萬元公帑   賑濟支那水災災民","createTime":"2018-08-10T14:49:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-11T14:14:15.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":43,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"8494aacb5cc4dd7b892db32fcbc7d485c341dfc4","tid":774760,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T14:49:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180810/large/1533899700_21b0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180810%2Flarge%2F1533899700_21b0.jpg&h=5ea94259&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n港共殖民政府公佈，接納賑災基金諮詢委員會的建議，從賑災基金批出65萬5,000元的撥款予香港樂施會，以賑濟支那甘肅省水災災民。撥款會用於為災民提供麵粉和食用油。委員會希望撥款能為災民提供適切援助，幫助他們早日回復正常生活。<br />\n<br />\n港共殖民政府發言人說，為確保撥款用於指定用途，委員會將要求香港樂施會在完成賑災計劃後，向委員會呈交評估報告及經審核的帳目。<br />\n<br />\n賑災基金諮詢委員會由政務司司長擔任主席，成員均由特首委任，包括財庫局局長、勞福局局長、民建聯葉國謙、鄉議局劉&zwj;業&zwj;強等。"},{"pid":"31c086ead76c17450c70dfdc61b0d7ceffccc306","tid":774760,"uid":138557,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T15:00:03.000Z","msg":"on9"},{"pid":"50b73a14fddae18f636b524480502e3be8f47649","tid":774760,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T15:01:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7578bc6a4bdd2463af06b15f2ad4c1589e615a6","tid":774760,"uid":3241,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T15:03:34.000Z","msg":"香港樂施會在完成賑災計劃後，向委員會呈交評估報告及經審核的帳目<br />\n<br />\n咩仲有戇鳩會信呢句<br />\n我地比支那呃左幾多次"},{"pid":"e9026c9d330bcf36bb1c46b002c9996f40f70bf8","tid":774760,"uid":153418,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T15:43:08.000Z","msg":"渣架捐咁少<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2420c73c1a564f4f8c7c6e4234ed4ad687d17081","tid":774760,"uid":179810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T07:19:21.000Z","msg":"邊個話cctvb唔報就唔洗捐<img src=\"/as